INSERT INTO `models` VALUES ('751c2becd0a24579a3ef6880b95de6bb','Diversified',250000.0000000000,'live','v1','Diversified All Weather Portfolio: this model is the most diversified strategy that we have. The base portfolio runs multiple trend following models on both the long and shorts side on etf\'s, stocks and commodities capturing short to longterm trends.  The second layer comprises of a series of inter-day trading algorithms (day trading) to create uncorrelated returns to trend following. The third layer incorporates buying call and put options to capture outsized returns from liquid stocks. The fourth layer shorts naked put options or straddles up to 50% of the portfolio to capture  the high yield from options premiums when implied volatility is high thereby created pnl when the market is range bound. Covered called can also be executed if the trend following stock component is deep in the money.  Lastly, we may from time to time execute out of money puts to protect the portfolio from market corrections. The combination of these strategies creates an All Weather Portfolio suitable for most market conditions.','All Weather: S&P 500 and Nasdaq ETFs as the base portfolio with liquid stocks and options.  Can trade global markets with US underlying as the base portfolio.','The portfolio can be 200% long and 100% short as calculated as all models in with stocks and options.  In practice the portfolio is under 100% of deployed cash due to the nature of the models active trading and avoiding risk.','Portfolio can be turned into cash in one day.','Monthly reporting by fund management team.','As calculated by Interactive Brokers',2.000000,20.000000,'[\"Options\", \"ETF\"]','15 days before month end notification','2026-07-03 01:48:11','2026-07-06 06:11:50'),('bf54ea96b34948758eb1c39d118ba446','Zero',250000.0000000000,'live','v3','This model uses advanced statistics and machine learning to capture inter-day price movements (day trading) of very liquid zero days to expiry options.  The model will buy naked calls and puts, buy call and out spreads and short call and out spreads at different times of the trading day. There is no overnight risk as the account is left in cash or T-bills or gold or any long term terming of your choosing as long as we maintenance a 10% cash buffer for pnl fluctuations.','Mainly index zero days to export options like S&P and Nasdaq.  Can also trade very liquid stock options.  Mainly US markets','Zero days to explore options are not measured in Leverage as the better measure is worst case daily loss due to short positions going into the money or long positions go to zero.  The targeted daily worse case is 5% of the portfolio.','Daily liquid','Monthly reporting by fund management team.','As calculated by Interactive Brokers',0.000000,30.000000,'[\"Options\"]','15 days before month end notification','2026-07-03 01:44:25','2026-07-06 05:09:38');
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `models` ENABLE KEYS */;
UNLOCK TABLES;

